articleContent: Reading Time:  < 1 minuteCounty Animal Services is rolling out its mobile veterinary bus to bring affordable pet health services such as spaying and neutering, dental work and other outpatient care to communities where it is most needed. Learn more about microchipping, rabies vaccine and spaying and neutering with County Animal Services and check to see if they are coming to your community soon.
